from discord import Embed, Colour
from discord.ext import commands
from datetime import datetime
import random
import asyncio

class FunCog(commands.Cog):
    def __init__(self, bot):
        self.bot = bot

    @commands.command(name='8ball')
    async def eight_ball(self, ctx, *, question):
        responses = [
            "Yes",
            "No",
            "Maybe",
            "Probably",
            "Not sure",
            "Ask again later",
            "Outlook good",
            "Outlook not so good",
            "I think not",
            "Most likely"
        ]
        answer = random.choice(responses)
        embed = Embed(title="8 Ball Answer", description=answer, color=Colour.blue())
        embed.set_footer(text=f"Question asked by {ctx.author.name}")
        await ctx.send(embed=embed)

    @commands.command(name='coinflip')
    async def coin_flip(self, ctx):
        result = random.choice(['Heads', 'Tails'])
        embed = Embed(title="Coin Flip Result", description=result, color=Colour.green())
        embed.set_footer(text=f"Flipped by {ctx.author.name}")
        await ctx.send(embed=embed)

    @commands.command(name='roll')
    async def roll_dice(self, ctx):
        roll = random.randint(1, 6)
        embed = Embed(title="Dice Roll", description=f"You rolled a **{roll}**", color=Colour.orange())
        embed.set_footer(text=f"Rolled by {ctx.author.name}")
        await ctx.send(embed=embed)

    @commands.command(name='flip')
    async def flip_coin(self, ctx):
        result = random.choice(['Heads', 'Tails'])
        embed = Embed(title="Coin Flip", description=result, color=Colour.green())
        embed.set_footer(text=f"Flipped by {ctx.author.name}")
        await ctx.send(embed=embed)

    @commands.command(name='choose')
    async def choose_between(self, ctx, *, options):
        options = options.split(',')
